10.7 Interactive: File Scan vs. Index Lookup






Tip



Drag the slider to change the number of rows. Observe how a full file scan grows linearly (O(n)) while a B+ tree index lookup grows only logarithmically (O(\log n)).



viewof rowCount = Inputs.range([1000, 1000000], {
  step: 1000,
  value: 100000,
  label: "Number of rows"
})







{
